'''{{lang|en|Android}}'''（讀音：英：{{ipa|['ændrɔɪd]}}，美：{{ipa|[ˈænˌdrɔɪd]}}），在香港通用原名「Android」，只有在中國和台灣等華人地區使用非官方名稱「安卓」，{{NoteTag|Android並沒有官方他國語言名稱，只有坊間的別稱。但中國版[[Wear_OS|Android Wear]]作業系統曾使用「你好，安卓」替代「Ok Google」以喚醒語音助理}}是一個基於[[Linux核心|Linux核心]]与其他[[开源软件|开源软件]]的[[開放原始碼|開放原始碼]]的[[行動作業系統|行動作業系統]]，由[[Google|谷歌]]成立的[[開放手機聯盟|開放手機聯盟]]持續領導與開發。

<!--起源與簡介-->
{{lang|en|Android Inc.}}於2003年10月由[[安迪·鲁賓|安迪·鲁賓]]、[[利奇·米納爾|利奇·米納爾]]、尼克·席爾斯、克里斯·懷特在[[加州|加州]][[帕羅奧圖|帕羅奧圖]]創建。Android最初由[[安迪·鲁賓|安迪·鲁賓]]等人開發製作<ref>[http://www.programmer.com.cn/3970/ Android之父Andy Rubin：生而Geek] {{Wayback|url=http://www.programmer.com.cn/3970/ |date=20110203145614 }}作者：Wuzhimin本文來自《程式員》雜誌2010年9期</ref>，最初開發這個系統的早期方向是創建一個[[數位相機|數位相機]]的先進作業系統，但是後來發現相機市場規模不夠大，加上智慧型手機發展趨勢快速成長，於是{{lang|en|Android}}成為一款面向智慧型手機的作業系統。於2005年7月11日{{lang|en|Android Inc.}}被[[美國|美國]]科技企業{{lang|en|Google}}收購<ref name="gba">{{cite web |url = http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/aug2005/tc20050817_0949_tc024.htm |title = Google Buys Android for Its Mobile Arsenal |publisher = Businessweek.com |date = 2005-08-17 |accessdate = 2010-10-29 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/5wk7sIvVb?url=http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/aug2005/tc20050817_0949_tc024.htm |archive-date = 2011-02-24 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="hh">{{cite web|url=http://www.romzj.com/posts/id-2603.htm|title=Google 收购 Android 十周年|publisher=romzj.com|accessdate=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715010738/http://www.romzj.com/posts/id-2603.htm|archive-date=2015-07-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

<!--開源及發展-->
2007年11月，{{lang|en|Google}}與84家硬體製造商、軟體開發商及電信營運商成立[[開放手機聯盟|開放手機聯盟]]來共同研發{{lang|en|Android}}，隨後，{{lang|en|Google}}以[[Apache許可證|Apache免費開放原始碼許可證]]的授權方式，發佈了{{lang|en|Android}}的原始碼<ref name="AndroidOverview">{{cite web |url = http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/android_overview.html |publisher = Open andset Alliance |accessdate = 2008-09-23 |title = Android Overview |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080923210309/http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/android_overview.html |archive-date = 2008-09-23 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，開放原始碼加速了{{lang|en|Android}}普及，讓生產商推出搭載{{lang|en|Android}}的智慧型手機<ref name="OHAhome">{{cite web |url = http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/ |title = Open Handset Alliance |accessdate = 2010-06-10 |publisher = Open Handset Alliance |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071107080329/http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/ |archive-date = 2007-11-07 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://phandroid.com/2008/12/10/sony-ericsson-htc-androids-set-for-summer-2009/ |title = Sony Ericsson, HTC Androids Set For Summer 2009 |work = Android Phone Fans |first = Rob |last = Jackson |date = 2008-12-10 |accessdate = 2009-09-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090524210443/http://phandroid.com/2008/12/10/sony-ericsson-htc-androids-set-for-summer-2009/ |archive-date = 2009-05-24 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="AndroidAnnouncement">{{cite press release |url = http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/press_110507.html |title = Industry Leaders Announce Open Platform for Mobile Devices |accessdate = 2007-11-05 |date = 2007-11-05 |publisher = [[Open_Handset_Alliance|Open Handset Alliance]] |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65rAj5GdL?url=http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/press_110507.html |archive-date = 2012-03-02 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url = http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/oha_faq.html |title = FAQ |accessdate = 2010-11-15 |publisher = [[Open_Handset_Alliance|Open Handset Alliance]] |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101123144140/http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/oha_faq.html |archive-date = 2010-11-23 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，{{lang|en|Android}}後來更逐漸拓展到平板電腦及其他領域上<ref>[http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/cn/opensource/os-android-devel／Android開發簡介]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} developerWorks IBM 2009年6月08日</ref>。

<!--發展簡述-->
2010年末數據顯示，僅正式推出兩年的{{lang|en|Android}}作業系統在市場佔有率上已經超越稱霸逾十年的[[諾基亞|諾基亞]]{{lang|en|[[Symbian|Symbian]]}}系統<ref name="canalysQ42010">{{cite web |url=http://www.canalys.com/newsroom/google%E2%80%99s-android-becomes-world%E2%80%99s-leading-smart-phone-platform |title=Google's Android becomes the world's leading smart phone platform |work=Canalys |date=2011-01-31 |accessdate=2012-02-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225091704/http://www.canalys.com/newsroom/google%E2%80%99s-android-becomes-world%E2%80%99s-leading-smart-phone-platform |archivedate=2012-02-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.canalys.com/pr/2011/r2011013.html |title = Google's Android becomes the world's leading smart phone platform (Canalys research release: r2011013) |work = Canalys |date = 2011-01-31 |accessdate = 2011-02-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110719121213/http://www.canalys.com/pr/2011/r2011013.html |archive-date = 2011-07-19 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，成為全球第一大智慧型手機作業系統<ref>[http://www.canalys.com/newsroom/android-takes-almost-50-share-worldwide-smart-phone-market Android市場份額已達48%] {{Wayback|url=http://www.canalys.com/newsroom/android-takes-almost-50-share-worldwide-smart-phone-market |date=20190427124101 }}Canalys數據2011/02/01</ref>。

在2014年[[Google_I/O|Google I/O]]開發者大會上{{lang|en|Google}}宣佈過去30天裡有10億台活躍的Android設備，相較於2013年6月則是5.38億<ref>[http://www.techspot.com/news/57228-google-shows-off-new-version-of-android-announces-1-billion-active-monthly-users.html Android過去1個月啟用裝置達10億台] {{Wayback|url=http://www.techspot.com/news/57228-google-shows-off-new-version-of-android-announces-1-billion-active-monthly-users.html |date=20181005091721 }}Android數據2014/06/25</ref>。

2017年3月，{{lang|en|Android}}全球網路流量和設備超越[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]，正式成為全球第一大作業系統<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gs.statcounter.com/press/android-overtakes-windows-for-first-time |title=Android overtakes Windows for first time |access-date=2019-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625232222/http://gs.statcounter.com/press/android-overtakes-windows-for-first-time |archive-date=2017-06-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

截至2022年5月，根據[[StatCounter|StatCounter]]統計，除了美國、英國、加拿大、挪威、瑞典、[[丹麥|丹麥]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]、[[科索沃|科索沃]]、日本、台灣和澳大利亞外，在其他所有國家和地區Android都是最被廣泛使用的[[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]作業系統<ref>{{Cite web|title=全球行動裝置作業系統市佔率|url=https://gs.statcounter.com/os-market-share/mobile/worldwide/#monthly-202205-202205-map|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=英语|archive-date=2022-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220601100814/https://gs.statcounter.com/os-market-share/mobile/worldwide|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

