2007年9月，數碼雜誌《Information Week》報導了一項Evalueserve的研究報告，指Google已在行動電話領域上提交了多份[[專利|專利]]申請<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.informationweek.com/news/showArticle.jhtml?articleID=201807587&cid=nl_IWK_daily |title=Google's Secret Patent Portfolio Predicts gPhone |last=Claburn |first=Thomas |work=[[InformationWeek|InformationWeek]] |date=2007-09-19 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080317142342/http://www.informationweek.com/news/showArticle.jhtml?articleID=201807587&cid=nl_IWK_daily |archivedate=2008-03-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=James Quintana |last=Pearce |title=Google’s Strong Mobile-Related Patent Portfolio |url=https://gigaom.com/2007/09/20/419-googles-strong-mobile-related-patent-portfolio/ |website=[[Gigaom|Gigaom]] |publisher=Knowingly, Corp. |date=2007-09-20 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313124031/https://gigaom.com/2007/09/20/419-googles-strong-mobile-related-patent-portfolio/ |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>。

2007年11月5日，在Google的領導下，成立了[[開放手機聯盟|開放手機聯盟]]（Open Handset Alliance），那是包括Google在內的科技公司聯盟，其他成員包括[[HTC|HTC]]、[[摩托羅拉|摩托羅拉]]、[[Samsung|Samsung]]等設備製造商，無線運營商則包括[[Sprint|Sprint]]及[[T-Mobile|T-Mobile]]，晶片製造商[[高通|高通]]及[[德州儀器|德州儀器]]，目標是為行動裝置開發「首個真正開放和全面的行動設備平台」<ref name="Announcement of OHA">{{cite web |title=Industry Leaders Announce Open Platform for Mobile Devices |url=http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/press_110507.html |website=[[Open_Handset_Alliance|Open Handset Alliance]] |date=2007-11-05 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65rAj5GdL?url=http://www.openhandsetalliance.com/press_110507.html |archivedate=2012-03-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Erick |last=Schonfeld |title=Breaking: Google Announces Android and Open Handset Alliance |url=https://techcrunch.com/2007/11/05/breaking-google-announces-android-and-open-handset-alliance/ |website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=2007-11-05 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622140334/https://techcrunch.com/2007/11/05/breaking-google-announces-android-and-open-handset-alliance/ |archivedate=2017-06-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Andy |last=Rubin |title=Where's my Gphone? |url=https://googleblog.blogspot.no/2007/11/wheres-my-gphone.html |website=Official Google Blog |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |date=2007-11-05 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313040638/https://googleblog.blogspot.no/2007/11/wheres-my-gphone.html |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>。隨後，其他廠商加入，包括[[Broadcom|Broadcom]]、[[Intel|Intel]]、[[LG|LG]]、[[Marvell_Technology_Group|Marvell]]等。聯盟開放手持裝置聯盟的建立目的是為了創建一個更加開放自由的行動電話環境。而在開放手持裝置聯盟創建的同一日，聯盟對外展示了他們的第一個產品：一部搭載了以Linux 2.6為核心基礎的Android作業系統的智慧型手機。該年內，開放手機聯盟正面對著另外兩個其他的[[開放源碼|開源碼]]的競爭對手，包括[[Symbian基金會|Symbian基金會]]和[[LiMo基金會|LiMo基金會]]，LiMo基金會開發了一個基於[[Linux|Linux]]的行動作業系統，就如Google。

2008年12月9日，新一批成員加入開放手持裝置聯盟，包括[[ARM|ARM]]、[[華為|華為]]、[[索尼移動|索尼]]等公司<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSN0928595620081210 |title=Corrected: Update 2: More mobile phone makers back Google's Android |last=Martinez |first=Jennifer |work=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |publisher=Thomson Reuters |date=2008-12-10 |accessdate=2008-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081213133154/http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSN0928595620081210 |archive-date=2008-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.businessweek.com/the_thread/techbeat/archives/2008/12/googles_android_2.html |title=Google's Android Gains More Powerful Followers |last=Kharif |first=Olga |work=[[BusinessWeek|BusinessWeek]] |publisher=[[McGraw-Hill|McGraw-Hill]] |date=2008-12-09 |accessdate=2008-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081213010107/http://www.businessweek.com/the_thread/techbeat/archives/2008/12/googles_android_2.html |archive-date=2008-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自2008年以來，Android已有許多更新以逐步改進其作業系統，並增加了新功能及修復了以前版本的錯誤。每個主要版本的名稱都以甜品或含糖的小食並按字母順序來命名，最初的幾個Android版本按此順序稱為「紙杯蛋糕（Cupcake）」、「甜甜圈（Donut）」、「閃電泡芙（Eclair）」和「優格霜淇淋（Froyo）」。

為了跟[[iPhone_3G|iPhone 3G]]能互相媲美，[[諾基亞|諾基亞]]和黑莓手機於2008年均宣布有關觸控螢幕的智能手機的資訊，Android的焦點最終也轉向觸控螢幕。第一款運行Android系統的商用智能手機是[[HTC_Dream|HTC Dream]]，亦名為T-Mobile G1，該智能手機於2008年9月23日發布<ref>{{cite web |first=Doug |last=Aamoth |title=T-Mobile officially announces the G1 Android phone |url=https://techcrunch.com/2008/09/23/t-mobile-officially-announces-the-g1-android-phone/ |website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=2008-09-23 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313042152/https://techcrunch.com/2008/09/23/t-mobile-officially-announces-the-g1-android-phone/ |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Richard |last=Gao |title=Android and its first purchasable product, the T-Mobile G1, celebrate their 8th birthdays today |url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2016/09/23/android-first-purchasable-product-t-mobile-g1-celebrate-8th-birthdays-today/ |website=Android Police |date=2016-09-23 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313045236/http://www.androidpolice.com/2016/09/23/android-first-purchasable-product-t-mobile-g1-celebrate-8th-birthdays-today/ |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>。

{{Anchor|AOSP}}<!-- [[AOSP|AOSP]]重定向至此，请勿移除 -->同時，一個負責持續發展Android作業系統的開源代碼專案成立了[[AOSP|AOSP]]（Android Open Source Project）。<ref name="source.android.com">{{cite web | url = http://source.android.com/about/index.html | title = About the Android Open Source Project | accessdate = 2010-11-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101118083908/http://source.android.com/about/index.html | archive-date = 2010-11-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>除了開放手持裝置聯盟之外，Android還擁有全球各地開發人員組成的開源社群來專門負責開發Android應用程式和第三方Android作業系統來延長和擴展Android的功能和性能。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.news.com/8301-13580_3-9815495-39.html | title = Google's Android parts ways with Java industry group | work = CNET News | first = Stephen | last = Shankland | date = 2007-11-12 | access-date = 2019-04-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080513073050/http://www.news.com/8301-13580_3-9815495-39.html | archive-date = 2008-05-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>[http://cn.engadget.com/2012/04/01/google-android-4-0-4-android/ Google將Android 4.0.4源代碼送交AOSP開源項目] {{Wayback|url=http://cn.engadget.com/2012/04/01/google-android-4-0-4-android/ |date=20180929023325 }}ENGADGET中國版2012</ref>

隨著2013年Android發布新版本[[Android_KitKat|奇巧巧克力]]，Google解釋「由於這些設備使我們的生活如此甜蜜，每個Android版本都以甜品來命名」，雖然Google的發言人在接受[[CNN|CNN]]訪談時指：「這有點像內部團隊的事情，我們更願意做多一點—我該怎樣說呢—我會說在這個問題上有點難以捉摸的<ref>{{cite web |first=Murali K. |last=Menon |title=Android Nougat: Here’s why Google names the OS after sweets |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/food-wine/from-donut-to-nougat-why-are-android-versions-named-after-sweets-2887237/ |website=[[The_Indian_Express|The Indian Express]] |publisher=[[Indian_Express_Limited|Indian Express Limited]] |date=2016-07-03 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313044156/http://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/food-wine/from-donut-to-nougat-why-are-android-versions-named-after-sweets-2887237/ |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>。」

2010年，Google推出了[[Google_Nexus|Nexus]]系列的裝置，他們與不同的合作設備製造商一起生產新設備並推出新的Android版本。該系列被形容為「透過引入新軟件迭代和硬件標準使其在Android的歷史中發揮了關鍵作用，並成為不會因"歷代的更新"導致軟件膨脹而聞名<ref>{{cite web |first=Florence |last=Ion |title=From Nexus One to Nexus 10: a brief history of Google’s flagship devices |url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2013/05/from-the-nexus-one-to-the-nexus-10-a-brief-history-of-nexus-devices/ |website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] |date=2013-05-15 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624004245/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2013/05/from-the-nexus-one-to-the-nexus-10-a-brief-history-of-nexus-devices/ |archivedate=2017-06-24 }}</ref>」。在2013年5月的[[Google_I/O|Google開發者大會]]上，他們宣佈了[[Samsung_Galaxy_S4|Samsung Galaxy S4]]的特別版，特別版在於它搭載了原生Android，並承諾能快速接收新的系統更新<ref>{{cite web |first=Sean |last=Hollister |title=Google turns the Samsung Galaxy S4 into a Nexus phone, coming June 26th for $649 |url=https://www.theverge.com/2013/5/15/4333716/galaxy-s4-stock-android-google-io-2013 |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |date=2013-05-15 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226220255/http://www.theverge.com/2013/5/15/4333716/galaxy-s4-stock-android-google-io-2013 |archivedate=2016-12-26 }}</ref>。裝置將成為「Google Play Edition」的開始，其他設備也會隨之而來，包括[[HTC_One_(M7)|HTC One (M7)]]以及[[Moto_G|Moto G]]<ref>{{cite web |first=Andrew |last=Cunningham |title=Moto G Google Play edition replaces near-stock Android with stock Android |url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/01/moto-g-google-play-edition-replaces-near-stock-android-with-stock-android/ |website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] |date=2014-01-14 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313042911/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/01/moto-g-google-play-edition-replaces-near-stock-android-with-stock-android/ |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>。2015年，Google Play Edition版步入了历史。

從2008至2013年，[[雨果·巴拉|雨果·巴拉]]擔任Android產品發言人，參與Google年度開發人員會議的[[Google_I/O|Google開發者大會]]。他於2013年8月離開Google，並隨即加入中國手機製造商[[小米集團|小米]]<ref>{{cite web |first=Mat |last=Smith |title=Android VP Hugo Barra leaves Google, joins Chinese phone maker Xiaomi (updated) |url=https://www.engadget.com/2013/08/28/android-vp-hugo-barra-report-leaves-google-xiaomi/ |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=2013-08-28 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313041804/https://www.engadget.com/2013/08/28/android-vp-hugo-barra-report-leaves-google-xiaomi/ |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Egan |last=Orion |title=Google's Android VP Hugo Barra joins Chinese phone maker Xiaomi |url=http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2291600/googles-android-vp-hugo-barra-joins-chinese-phone-maker-xiaomi |website=[[The_Inquirer|The Inquirer]] |publisher=[[Incisive_Media|Incisive Media]] |date=2013-08-28 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313041606/http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2291600/googles-android-vp-hugo-barra-joins-chinese-phone-maker-xiaomi |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>。在他離任不足六個月前，Google時任[[行政總裁|CEO]][[賴利·佩吉|賴利·佩吉]]在一篇博客文章中宣佈，[[安迪·鲁賓|鲁賓]]從Android部門轉移到Google的新項目，而[[桑德爾·皮蔡|桑德爾·皮蔡]]將會成為Android的新主管<ref>{{cite web |first=Larry |last=Page |title=Update from the CEO |url=https://googleblog.blogspot.no/2013/03/update-from-ceo.html |website=Official Google Blog |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |date=2013-03-13 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313043456/https://googleblog.blogspot.no/2013/03/update-from-ceo.html |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Charles |last=Arthur |title=Andy Rubin moved from Android to take on 'moonshots' at Google |url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/mar/13/andy-rubin-google-move |website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]] |date=2013-03-13 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312004957/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/mar/13/andy-rubin-google-move |archivedate=2017-03-12 }}</ref>。皮蔡本人最終轉換了職位，隨著Google重組大型聯合的[[Alphabet|Alphabet]]集團<ref>{{cite web |first=Russell |last=Brandom |title=Google is reorganizing and Sundar Pichai will become new CEO |url=https://www.theverge.com/2015/8/10/9128083/sundar-pichai-ceo-google-larry-page-sergey-brin |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |date=2015-08-10 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313042225/http://www.theverge.com/2015/8/10/9128083/sundar-pichai-ceo-google-larry-page-sergey-brin |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Jessica |last=Conditt |title=Google gets an overhaul and a new CEO: Sundar Pichai |url=https://www.engadget.com/2015/08/10/google-gets-an-overhaul-and-a-new-ceo-sundar-pichai/ |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=2015-08-10 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313041506/https://www.engadget.com/2015/08/10/google-gets-an-overhaul-and-a-new-ceo-sundar-pichai/ |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>，他在2015年8月成為了Google的新任CEO，讓{{le|浩史·洛克海默|Hiroshi Lockheimer}}成為Android的新任負責人<ref>{{cite web |first=Mark |last=Bergen |title=New Google CEO Sundar Pichai Makes First Major Executive Picks |url=http://www.recode.net/2015/10/9/11619448/new-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-makes-first-major-executive-picks |website=[[Recode|Recode]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |date=2015-10-09 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170114190148/http://www.recode.net/2015/10/9/11619448/new-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-makes-first-major-executive-picks |archivedate=2017-01-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Andrew |last=Martonik |title=Sundar Pichai promotes Hiroshi Lockheimer to oversee Android, Chrome OS and Chromecast |url=http://www.androidcentral.com/sundar-pichai-promotes-hiroshi-lockheimer-oversee-android-chrome-os-and-chromecast |website=Android Central |publisher=Mobile Nations |date=2015-10-09 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223132142/http://www.androidcentral.com/sundar-pichai-promotes-hiroshi-lockheimer-oversee-android-chrome-os-and-chromecast |archivedate=2017-02-23 }}</ref>。

