== 系統特點 ==
=== 界面 ===

Android的預設用戶界面主要基於直接操作，透過觸控鬆散地對應現實動作以作出輸入，例如滑動、點擊、捏動和反向擠壓，隨著[[虛擬鍵盤|虛擬鍵盤]]，以操控屏幕上的物件<ref>{{cite web |title=Touch Devices |url=http://source.android.com/tech/input/touch-devices.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120125061950/http://source.android.com/tech/input/touch-devices.html |website=Android Open Source Project |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |archivedate=2012-01-25 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[遊戲控制器|遊戲控制器]]及物理鍵盤都能透過[[藍牙|藍牙]]或[[USB|USB]]得到支援<ref>{{cite web |title=Handling Controller Actions |url=https://developer.android.com/training/game-controllers/controller-input.html |website=Android Developers |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312195206/https://developer.android.com/training/game-controllers/controller-input.html |archivedate=2017-03-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Handling Keyboard Input |url=https://developer.android.com/training/keyboard-input/index.html |website=Android Developers |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313041058/https://developer.android.com/training/keyboard-input/index.html |archivedate=2017-03-13 }}</ref>。在回應用家的輸入方面，設計旨在提供立即流暢的觸摸界面，經常使用設備的振動功能向用戶提供觸覺反饋。內部硬件，例如是[[加速規|加速規]]、[[陀螺儀|陀螺儀]]、[[接近傳感器|距離傳感器]]都能被某些應用程式來回應用戶的操作，例如根據裝置的方向來把屏幕由縱向調整為橫向<ref>{{cite web |title=Sensors Overview |url=https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/sensors/sensors_overview.html |website=Android Developers |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216064514/https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/sensors/sensors_overview.html |archivedate=2017-02-16 }}</ref>，或容許用戶透過旋轉裝置，在[[競速遊戲|賽車遊戲]]中駕駛車輛<ref>{{cite web |first=Chris |last=Chavez |title=Real Racing 2 Speeds Into The Android Market – Leaves Part 1 In The Dust |url=http://phandroid.com/2011/12/22/real-racing-2-speeds-into-the-android-market-leaves-part-1-in-the-dust/ |website=Phandroid |date=2011-12-22 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219030819/http://phandroid.com/2011/12/22/real-racing-2-speeds-into-the-android-market-leaves-part-1-in-the-dust/ |archivedate=2017-02-19 }}</ref>。

當Android裝置啟動就會進入主畫面，那是裝置的主要導航及信息「樞紐」，類似於個人電腦的[[桌面比擬|桌面]]。Android的主畫面通常由應用程序圖標及小工具（widget）組成，應用程序圖標啟動相關的應用程序，而小工具則會實時顯示，並會自動更新內容，例如[[天氣預報|天氣預報]]、用戶的電子郵件，或是直接在主畫面上看新聞摘要<ref>{{cite web |title=Widgets |url=https://developer.android.com/design/patterns/widgets.html |website=Android Developers |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312200056/https://developer.android.com/design/patterns/widgets.html |archivedate=2017-03-12 }}</ref>。主畫面可以由若干頁面組成，用戶可以在這些頁面之間來回滑動<ref name="Design info"/>。[[Google_Play|Google Play]]上提供的第三方應用程式，而其他的應用程式商店可以廣泛使用重新定義的
主畫面[[主題包|主題包]]<ref>{{cite web |first=Joe |last=Hindy |title=15 best Android launcher apps of 2017 |url=http://www.androidauthority.com/best-android-launcher-apps-222408/ |website=Android Authority |date=2017-02-04 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501192958/http://www.androidauthority.com/best-android-launcher-apps-222408 |archivedate=2017-05-01 }}</ref>，甚至模仿其他作業系統的外觀，例如[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]<ref>{{cite web |first=Whitson |last=Gordon |title=Launcher 7 Brings Windows Phone's Simple, Attractive Interface to Android |url=http://lifehacker.com/5804091/launcher-7-brings-windows-phones-simple-attractive-interface-to-android |website=[[Lifehacker|Lifehacker]] |publisher=[[Univision_Communications|Univision Communications]] |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108143524/http://lifehacker.com/5804091/launcher-7-brings-windows-phones-simple-attractive-interface-to-android |archivedate=2017-01-08 }}</ref>。大多數製造商會定制他們Android設備的外觀和功能，以從競爭對手中脫穎而出<ref>{{cite web |first=Daniel A. |last=Begun |title=Looking at the Android operating system |url=http://www.dummies.com/consumer-electronics/smartphones/droid/looking-at-the-android-operating-system/ |website=[[For_Dummies|For Dummies]] |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312195620/http://www.dummies.com/consumer-electronics/smartphones/droid/looking-at-the-android-operating-system/ |archivedate=2017-03-12 }}</ref>。

屏幕頂部是狀態欄，顯示有關裝置及其連接的資訊。用戶可把狀態欄「拉下」，以顯示應用程式顯示的重要信息，或屏幕更新的通知<ref name="Design info">{{cite web |title=Phones & Tablets |url=https://developer.android.com/design/handhelds/index.html |website=Android Developers |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331154020/https://developer.android.com/design/handhelds/index.html |archivedate=2017-03-31 }}</ref>。通知是「當用戶的應用程序在非使用時所提供簡短、及時和相關的訊息<ref>{{cite web |title=Notifications |url=https://material.io/guidelines/patterns/notifications.html |website=Material Design |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |accessdate=2017-03-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322170613/https://material.io/guidelines/patterns/notifications.html |archivedate=2017-03-22 }}</ref>。」當點擊了，用戶會被引導到該app內與該通知相關的屏幕。從[[Android_Jelly_Bean|Android Jelly Bean]]開始，可擴展通知「允許用戶透過點擊通知上的圖標，以便它擴展和顯示從通知中得知的更多信息以及有可能的應用操作<ref>{{cite web |title=Notifications |url=http://developer.android.com/design/patterns/notifications.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121208022602/http://developer.android.com/design/patterns/notifications.html |website=Android Developers |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |archivedate=2012-12-08 |accessdate=2017-03-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

「所有應用程序」的屏幕將會所有已安裝的應用程式，用戶可以將應用程序從列表拖曳到主畫面上。「最近」的屏幕讓用戶在最近使用過的應用程序之間進行切換<ref name="Design info"/>。

